0.2.0
-----
Most important:
- Moved examples to README.
- File renames:
    *c*   -> *vacf*
    *fft* -> *pdos*
- Output PDOS which is normalized (integral area).
- Implemented Direct Method (there is no official name) as alternative to
  FFT(vacf) for calculating the PDOS.
- Renamed option -t -> -f
- new option: -t for choosing the DOS calculation method.

other:
- Moved cmd line args parsing code out of main() to __main__ 
  on module level.    

0.2.1
-----
Some doc updates. Added support for gzip compressed pw.x outfiles.
Test for vacf_pdos() and direct_pdos() in test/.
changeset:   11:83cdcd4bebb3

0.2.2
-----
lib/Makefile
    Use gfortran per default and some custom AMD Phenom X4 options.
lib/pydos.py
    Make regular expressions match all kinds of strings representing
    floats.
    Introduced default option handling to main(): get_parser().
    get_default_opts().


